iption": "Powerful Meditation Mantra to Overcome Fear | Aadays Tisai Aadays | Meditation Mantra Chanting\n\nThis mantra is believed to instill the entire knowledge of the Universe without ever reading a book. Meditation with this mantra rids you of fears and prepare you for merging with the Creator - the Infinite Source of us All.\n\n\nMANTRA + MEANING\n\nAadays Tisai Adays, \nAad Aneel Anaad Anaahat, \nJug Jug Ayko Vays\n\nI bow to him, I humbly bow,\nThe primal one, the Pure Light, without beginning, without end\nThroughout all the Ages, He is One and the Same\n\n=====\n\n☯ MANTRA MEDITATION MONTH\n\nAt Meditative Mind, we are dedicated in creating Music for Healing Chakras,  Chakra Chants, Healing Meditation Mantras, And Relaxation Music .\nAnd this Month is dedicated to MANTRA Meditations\nWe are featuring various Mantras for Meditation, Mantras for Healing, Mantra for Positive Energy, for Protection, for Removing Obstacles, Mantra for Success, Mantra for Bringing Peace,  and many more. We have recently released our favorite Mantra - OM Meditation. Here is our Mantra Meditation Playlist\nhttps://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsuCfYXzi5DLQmw5DbidL4xfFk2bNHXuq\n\n\n☯ SCHEDULE \nNew Videos Released on Mondays, Wednesdays, Thursdays, Sundays between\n5AM to 8AM(PST)\n\n☯ SUBSCRIBE for updates\nhttp://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=TheMeditativeMind\n\n\n☯ MEDITATIVE MIND CHANNEL\nhttps://www.youtube.com/user/TheMeditativeMind\n\n\n☯ CREDITS\nComposition, Music & Vocals by : Dilpreet Bhatia\n\n=============\n\"Our Mission is to bring more peace and mindfulness in people's lives through Music for Meditation, Chakra Healing, Mantra Meditation and Chants\"", "channel_id": "UCM0YvsRfYfsniGAhjvYFOSA", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM0YvsRfYfsniGAhjvYFOSA", "duration": 3749, "view_count": 15914, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8sI2EtjoG4", "categories": ["Music"], "tags": ["meditation mantra", "mantra medit